%% Circuit breaker state machine — single breaker, many codes
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Armed: engine start

    Armed --> TrippedMinor: minor breach<br/>stale_tick · wide_spread · stale_md
    TrippedMinor --> Armed: cooldown elapsed<br/>BREAKER_MINOR_COOLDOWN_SEC

    Armed --> TrippedMajor: major breach<br/>drawdown · reconcile · operator_halt
    TrippedMajor --> Latched: flatten triggered<br/>auto or operator

    Latched --> Armed: POST /breakers/rearm<br/>operator clear

    state TrippedMinor {
        [*] --> VetoEntries
        VetoEntries --> AutoResume: breaker.tick()
    }

    state TrippedMajor {
        [*] --> PauseAndFlatten
        PauseAndFlatten --> BlockEntries: engine scope blocked
        Note right of BlockEntries: reduce_only still allowed
    }

    note right of Armed
        PreTradeValidator checks breaker
        before every entry signal
    end note
